  <refpurpose>abort the current transaction</refpurpose>
 </refnamediv>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
 <refnamediv>
  <refname>ABORT</refname>
  <refpurpose>中止当前事务</refpurpose>
 </refnamediv>

 <refsynopsisdiv>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<synopsis>
ABORT [ WORK | TRANSACTION ]
</synopsis>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<synopsis>
ABORT [ WORK | TRANSACTION ]
</synopsis>
 </refsynopsisdiv>

 <refsect1>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <title>Description</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <title>描述</title>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <para>
   <command>ABORT</command> rolls back the current transaction and causes
   all the updates made by the transaction to be discarded.
   This command is identical
   in behavior to the standard <acronym>SQL</acronym> command
   <xref linkend="SQL-ROLLBACK">,
   and is present only for historical reasons.
  </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   <command>ABORT</command>回滚当前事务并且导致由该事务所作的所有更新被丢弃。这个命令的行为与标准<acronym>SQL</acronym>命令<xref linkend="SQL-ROLLBACK"/>的行为一样，并且只是为了历史原因存在。
  </para>
 </refsect1>

 <refsect1>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <title>Parameters</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <title>参数</title>

  <variablelist>
   <varlistentry>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
    <term><literal>WORK</literal></term>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
    <term><literal>WORK</literal></term>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
    <term><literal>TRANSACTION</literal></term>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
    <term><literal>TRANSACTION</literal></term>
    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
     <para>
      Optional key words. They have no effect.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      可选关键词。它们没有效果。
     </para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
 </refsect1>

 <refsect1>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <title>Notes</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <title>注解</title>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <para>
   Use <xref linkend="SQL-COMMIT"> to
   successfully terminate a transaction.
  </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   使用<xref linkend="SQL-COMMIT"/>成功地终止一个事务。
  </para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <para>
   Issuing <command>ABORT</> outside of a transaction block
   emits a warning and otherwise has no effect.
  </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   在一个事务块之外发出<command>ABORT</command>会发出一个警告消息并且不会产生效果。
  </para>
 </refsect1>

 <refsect1>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <title>Examples</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <title>例子</title>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <para>
   To abort all changes:
<programlisting>
ABORT;
</programlisting></para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   中止所有更改：
<programlisting>
ABORT;
</programlisting></para>
 </refsect1>

 <refsect1>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <title>Compatibility</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <title>兼容性</title>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <para>
   This command is a <productname>PostgreSQL</productname> extension
   present for historical reasons. <command>ROLLBACK</command> is the
   equivalent standard SQL command.
  </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   这个命令是一个因为历史原因而存在的<productname>PostgreSQL</productname>扩展。<command>ROLLBACK</command>是等效的标准 SQL 命令。
  </para>
 </refsect1>

